---
// UpgradeFounder — "Built from the bay, not a boardroom."
// Voice-rule line per SITE_CONTEXT.md — keep verbatim.
---
<!-- FOUNDER SECTION -->
<section id="founder" class="relative border-b border-line">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-24">
    <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Who builds this</span>
    <h2 class="mt-5 text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.6rem] leading-[1.05] font-bold">
      Built from the bay, <span class="text-accent">not a boardroom.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-7 space-y-5 text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed text-text-soft max-w-2xl">
      <p>
        I'm Bill, the owner of Designed to Elevate in Zanesville, Ohio.
      </p>
      <p>
        Before this became an agency, I was doing the work inside a real local shop — building Fitchin's website, improving the quote flow, helping with ads, reviews, and customer experience.
      </p>
      <p>
        That changed how I see websites.
      </p>
      <p>
        A good local business website isn't just a pretty homepage. It should answer questions, build trust, reduce friction, and help customers take the next step.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text font-medium">
        That's what I build.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="#apply" class="btn-primary">
        Get My Free 10-Minute Website Review
        <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
      <button type="button" data-call-text class="btn-ghost">
        Or text Bill directly
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- /FOUNDER SECTION -->
